7076.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bangladesh%20opposition%20calls%20for%20poll%20boycott%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703122058000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106167143%2Cimgsize-40334.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladesh-opposition-calls-for-poll-boycott%2Farticleshow%2F106167075.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106167075.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBangladesh's%20main%20opposition%20party%20urged%20voters%20Wednesday%20to%20boycott%20what%20it%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bone-sided%20dummy%20election%26quot%3B%20due%20in%20January%2C%20as%20PM%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20kicked%20off%20her%20campaign%20for%20a%20fourth%20consecutive%20term.%20With%20its%20leaders%20either%20jailed%20or%20in%20exile%2C%20opposition%20BNP%20has%20been%20calling%20for%20Hasina%20to%20resign%20and%20for%20a%20neutral%20authority%20to%20oversee%20the%20polls%2C%20which%20BNP%20is%20not%20contesting.%20%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%26quot%3BBoycott%20the%20dummy%20election%20on%20January%207.%20Don't%20participate%20in%20the%20monkey%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20BNP's%20senior%20joint%20secretary%20general%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladesh-opposition-calls-for-poll-boycott%2Farticleshow%2F106167075.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladesh-opposition-calls-for-poll-boycott%2Famp_articleshow%2F106167075.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fbangladesh-opposition-calls-for-poll-boycott%2Famp_articleshow%2F106167075.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHospitalisations%20Will%20Go%20Up%20As%20Covid%20Burden%20Increases%26quot%3B%3A%20Soumya%20Swaminathan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20year-and-a-half%20after%20India%20witnessed%20the%20Omicron%20wave%2C%20two%20eminent%20health%20experts%20have%20sounded%20a%20warning%20over%20the%20increasing%20Covid-19%20cases%20in%20India%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20JN.1%20sub-variant%20of%20Omicron%20being%20detected%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Dr%20Rajeev%20Jayadevan%2C%20Co-Chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20Covid%20Task%20Force%2C%20said%2030%25%20of%20all%20patients%20with%20influenza-like%20illnesses%20who%20were%20tested%20have%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20Covid%20positive%20in%20the%20Kochi%20region%20in%20a%20span%20of%20about%2024%20hours.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20Covid%20cases%20have%20spread%20into%20the%20community%20and%20that%20his%20neighbour%20has%20also%20tested%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Soumya%20Swaminathan%2C%20former%20WHO%20chief%20scientist%20-%20who%20also%20spoke%20exclusively%20to%20NDTV%20-%20has%20cautioned%20against%20dismissing%20Covid%20as%20a%20common%20cold%2C%20not%20just%20because%20of%20the%20people%20who%20fall%20severely%20ill%2C%20but%20because%20of%20the%20disease's%20long-term%20effects%2C%20including%20increased%20risk%20of%20heart%20attacks%2C%20strokes%20and%20mental%20health%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20experts%2C%20however%2C%20emphasised%20that%20the%20variant%2C%20while%20more%20transmissible%2C%20may%20not%20cause%20a%20high%20number%20of%20hospitalisations%2C%20partly%20because%20of%20India's%20high%20vaccination%20rate.%20Dr%20Swaminathan%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20India's%20health%20systems%20have%20come%20a%20long%20way%20from%20how%20they%20were%20during%20the%20first%20wave%20in%202020%20and%20the%20deadlier%20Delta%20wave%20in%202021%2C%20and%20the%20country%20is%20well%20prepared%20to%20handle%20an%20uptick%20in%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Swaminathan%20also%20listed%20out%20the%20precautions%20that%20people%20can%20take%20and%20stressed%20on%20the%20need%20for%20the%20elderly%20and%20those%20with%20poor%20immunity%20to%20start%20masking%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEntered%20The%20Community%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20data%2C%20India%20has%20seen%2021%20cases%20of%20the%20JN.1%20sub-variant%20so%20far%20-%2019%20in%20Goa%20and%20one%20each%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20spread%20of%20Covid%2C%20Dr%20Jayadevan%2C%20who%20posted%20a%20chart%20on%20X%20illustrating%20the%20rise%20in%20cases%20since%20November%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%20month%20or%20so%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Covid%20cases%20has%20been%20creeping%20up.%20But%2C%20as%20you%20know%2C%20testing%20in%20our%20country%20is%20quite%20low%2C%20close%20to%20zero%20in%20many%20places%20for%20many%20reasons...%20But%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20statistics%20as%20I%20posted%20on%20the%20graph%20from%20September%2C%20October%2C%20November%20and%20December%2C%20there%20is%20a%20sharp%20uptick%20sometime%20in%20November.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20November%2C%20it%20is%20only%20around%201%25%20of%20influenza-like%20illnesses%20showing%20positive%20for%20Covid%2C%20which%20is%20practically%20zero.%20But%2C%20from%20November%20onwards%2C%20we%20have%20had%20about%209%25.%20And%2C%20in%20December%2C%20after%20the%20meeting%20that%20concluded%20last%20night%2C%20it%20was%2030%25.%20And%20this%20data%20is%20from%20multiple%20hospitals%20in%20the%20(Kochi)%20region.%20So%20this%20shows%20that%20Covid%20is%20taking%20a%20greater%20share%20of%20what%20we%20call%20influenza-like%20illness%2C%20which%20basically%20means%20things%20like%20respiratory%20problems%2C%20breathing%20trouble%2C%20cough%2C%20fever%20and%20body%20ache%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jayadevan%20said%20that%20while%20JN.1%20is%20considered%20the%20fastest-rising%20variant%2C%20it%20does%20not%20necessarily%20mean%20more%20cases%20but%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bdominating%20the%20Covid%20landscape%26quot%3B.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20cases%20are%20increasing%2C%20people%20are%20being%20able%20to%20treat%20the%20symptoms%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20there%20is%20a%20community-wide%20spread%20of%20the%20JN.1%20variant%2C%20the%20Covid%20Task%20Force%20co-chair%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20much%20in%20the%20community.%20My%20neighbour%20has%20tested%20positive%20just%20this%20evening.%20So%20it%20is%20everywhere...%20But%20it%20is%20not%20causing%20a%20huge%20surge%20in%20hospitalisation.%20So%20that's%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Waves%20of%20Infection'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Dr%20Soumya%20Swaminathan%20was%20asked%20about%2030%25%20of%20pneumonia%20cases%20in%20Kochi%20hospitals%20turning%20out%20to%20be%20Covid%20positive%20and%20the%20likelihood%20of%20this%20being%20replicated%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20through%20this%20many%20times%20before%2C%20as%20you%20know%2C%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years.%20This%20is%20what%20we%20expected%20and%20this%20is%20what%20the%20WHO%20had%20talked%20about.%20Even%20when%20WHO%20Director-General%20Dr%20Tedros%20Ghebreyesus%20announced%20the%20end%20of%20the%20global%20public%20health%20emergency%20in%20May%20this%20year%2C%20he%20did%20say%20it%20is%20still%20a%20global%20health%20threat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20what%20we%20are%20seeing%20now.%20We're%20seeing%20a%20new%20variant%2C%20the%20JN.1%2C%20which%20is%20a%20sub-variant%20of%20Omicron.%20So%20hopefully%20it%20behaves%20like%20Omicron%2C%20which%20was%20relatively%20mild.%20But%20what%20happens%20is%20that%20every%20new%20variant%20gets%20some%20properties%20of%20being%20more%20transmissible.%20It%20is%20able%20to%20evade%20or%20avoid%20the%20antibody%20responses%20that%20we%20already%20have%20in%20our%20system.%20And%20therefore%20it%20is%20able%20to%20create%20these%20waves%20of%20infection%20where%20it%20infects%20people%20who've%20already%20been%20infected%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Swaminathan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20WHO%20chief%20scientist%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20global%20health%20body%20has%20classified%20JN.1%20as%20a%20variant%20of%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20coming%20to%20India%2C%20as%20you%20mentioned%2C%20we've%20just%20started%20increasing%20the%20testing.%20So%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20I%20think%20we%20will%20see%20more%20data%20coming%20from%20many%20states.%20Right%20now%2C%20it%20looks%20like%20a%20few%20states%20like%20Kerala%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20perhaps%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20they%20are%20reporting%20an%20uptick%20of%20cases%20and%20high%20positivity%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESymptoms%2C%20Time%20To%20Mask%20Up%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jayadevan%20said%20vaccines%20may%20have%20helped%20keep%20Covid%20at%20bay%20since%20the%20last%20wave%2C%20but%20a%20concern%20arises%20when%20a%20variant%20is%20markedly%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20JN.1%20is%20not%20like%20a%20one-step%20ahead%20variant.%20This%20is%20a%20multi-step%20ahead%20variant.%20We%20call%20it%20the%20saltation%20event%20in%20genetics%2C%20which%20basically%20means%20a%20pile%20of%20mutations%20suddenly%20occurring%20at%20one%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20masking%20up%2C%20the%20doctor%20advised%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20if%20you%20are%20trapped%20in%20a%20situation%20where%20it's%20ventilated%2C%20closed%2C%20crowded%2C%20you%20feel%20the%20air%20is%20still%20and%20there%20are%20people%20around%20you%2C%20it's%20safer%20to%20wear%20a%20mask.%20If%20you%20are%20travelling%20in%20a%20vehicle%20with%20multiple%20people%20who%20you%20don't%20know%2C%20wear%20a%20mask%20or%20at%20least%20roll%20your%20windows%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20recommended%20wearing%20a%20mask%20in%20closed%20spaces%20with%20many%20people%2C%20especially%20for%20those%20who%20are%20elderly%20and%20immunosuppressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Swaminathan%20said%20the%20symptoms%20of%20the%20new%20variant%20are%20fever%2C%20cough%2C%20loss%20of%20smell%20and%20loss%20of%20taste.%20She%20also%20pointed%20to%20persistent%20high%20fever%2C%20breathing%20difficulties%2C%20fatigue%2C%20inability%20to%20eat%20and%20a%20tendency%20to%20vomit%20as%20the%20warning%20signs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20recommended%20masking%20up%20in%20a%20crowded%20place%20if%20people%20are%20vulnerable%20to%20infections%20and%20also%20stressed%20that%20people%20who%20are%20sick%20should%20wear%20a%20mask%20to%20protect%20others.%20For%20the%20vulnerable%20population%2C%20she%20recommended%20using%20pulse%20oximeters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20A%20Common%20Cold%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20people%20comparing%20the%20newer%20variants%20of%20Covid%20with%20the%20common%20cold%2C%20Dr%20Swaminathan%20had%20a%20warning%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20different%20from%20the%20common%20cold%2C%20not%20just%20because%20of%20people%20getting%20severely%20ill%20with%20acute%20Covid%20pneumonia%2C%20but%20also%20because%20of%20the%20long-term%20effects%20of%20Covid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20we%20have%20enough%20data%20now%20from%20around%20the%20world%20to%20know%20that%20people%20who%20have%20suffered%20from%20Covid%20and%2C%20particularly%20those%20who%20have%20repeat%20infections%2C%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20get%2C%20for%20example%2C%20heart%20attacks%2C%20strokes%2C%20diabetes%2C%20dementia%2C%20depression%2C%20mental%20health%20problems%2C%20prolonged%20fatigue%20and%20muscle%20pain...%20inability%20to%20go%20back%20to%20their%20usual%20state%20of%20functioning%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Swaminathan%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20big%20difference%20between%20a%20common%20cold%20and%20Covid.%20So%20I%20would%20say%20let's%20not%20take%20it%20lightly.%20If%20you%20can%20avoid%20the%20infection%2C%20much%20better%20to%20avoid%20it%20than%20to%20get%20it%20and%20risk%20the%20after-effects%20of%20long%20Covid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpread%20Pattern%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jayadevan%20said%20India%20is%20unlikely%20to%20witness%20a%20uniform%20spread.%20Pointing%20to%20the%20current%20cases%20of%20the%20new%20variant%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTypically%2C%20Covid%20spreads%20in%20high%20travel%20zones%2C%20which%20are%20travel%20hubs%2C%20Kerala%20is%20a%20travel%20hub%2C%20so%20is%20Maharashtra%2C%20Mumbai%20area%2C%20Goa%20is%20a%20travel%20hub.%20We%20got%2018%20sequences%20of%20the%20JN.1%20from%20Goa.%20So%20I%20would%20imagine%20it%20will%20spread%20in%20these%20zones%20first%20and%20then%20slowly%20trickle%20into%20the%20other%20areas%20as%20people%20travel%20more%20and%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Swaminathan%20pointed%20out%20that%20by%20the%20time%20variants%20are%20detected%2C%20they%20are%20usually%20already%20spreading%20in%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20so%20it's%20likely%20that%20it's%20everywhere%3B%20and%20the%20more%20we%20test%2C%20the%20more%20we're%20going%20to%20find.%20In%20fact%2C%20wastewater%20surveillance%20being%20done%20in%20many%20countries%20suggests%20that%20this%20is%20going%20to%20become%20the%20dominant%20variant%20globally%20within%20the%20next%20week%20or%20so.%20So%20I%20think%20it%20is%20to%20be%20expected.%20I%20think%20what%20is%20important%20is%20for%20us%20to%20keep%20a%20close%20eye%20on%20what%20the%20clinical%20manifestations%20are.%20At%20the%20moment%2C%20it%20doesn't%20appear%20that%20it's%20causing%20any%20more%20severe%20illness%20than%20the%20previous%20Omicron%20variant%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmphasising%20the%20need%20to%20stay%20prepared%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20I%20think%20what%20happens%20is%20if%20you%20get%20a%20thousand%20cases%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20percentage%20of%20people%2C%20even%20if%20it's%201%25%2C%20who%20get%20very%20ill%2C%20who%20are%20in%20in%20the%20hospital.%20If%20you%20get%201%2C00%2C000%20cases%2C%20that%20many%20more%20people%20are%20going%20to%20get%20very%20ill%20and%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20particularly%20those%20over%20the%20age%20of%2065%20and%20those%20who%20have%20other%20comorbidities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20a%20good%20idea%20to%20be%20prepared%2C%20to%20take%20precautions%20so%20that%20we%20can%20at%20least%20protect%20those%20who%20are%20at%20highest%20risk%20of%20getting%20sick%20and%20prevent%20them%20from%20getting%20pneumonia%20and%20getting%20into%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVaccines%20Working%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Jayadevan%20said%20India%20is%20a%20well-vaccinated%20country%20and%20uses%20different%20vaccines%20than%20in%20the%20West%2C%20so%20data%20from%20those%20countries%20may%20not%20directly%20apply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20need%20for%20boosters%2C%20Dr%20Swaminathan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFrom%20what%20we%20are%20seeing%20around%20the%20world%2C%20I%20think%20vaccines%20are%20still%20working.%20It%20is%20very%20remarkable%20that%20they%20are%20still%20providing%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20protection%2C%20especially%20against%20severe%20disease...%20But%20again%2C%20for%20those%20who%20are%20very%20old%2C%20for%20those%20who%20have%20poor%20immunity%2C%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20that%20their%20immunity%20would%20have%20waned%2C%20that%20boosters%20might%20be%20needed%20at%20some%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20Prepared%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Swaminathan%20said%20doctors%20know%20how%20to%20treat%20Covid%20now%20and%20things%20are%20very%20different%20from%20how%20they%20were%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20preparation%20of%20the%20hospitals%20is%20important.%20I%20think%20mock%20drills%20have%20happened%20in%20many%20states%20to%20test%20the%20responses%20as%20well%20as%20to%20test%20the%20adequacy%20and%20functioning%20of%20the%20oxygen%2C%20the%20ventilators%2C%20all%20those%20things%20that%20we%20had%20prepared.%20So%2C%20in%20a%20way%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20test%20for%20our%20system%20to%20do%20this%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20to%20be%20absolutely%20ready%20and%20prepared%20and%20not%20have%20any%20nasty%20surprises%20when%20we%20actually%20need%20to%20use%20all%20of%20those%20things%20that%20we%20have%20invested%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20I%20believe%20that%20we%20are%20very%20well%20prepared%2C%20but%20that%20every%20state%20must%20exercise%20these%20precautions%20as%20well%20as%20mock%20drills%20and%20make%20sure%20that%2C%20even%20in%20remote%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20provide%20oxygen%20to%20people%20who%20need%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703122020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-04%2Ftrinpfdo_covid_650x400_14_April_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdr-soumya-swaminathan-jn-1-covid-variant-30-of-those-with-flu-like-illnesses-in-kochi-hospitals-are-covid-positive-top-expert-4712147%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20a%20year-and-a-half%20after%20India%20witnessed%20the%20Omicron%20wave%2C%20two%20eminent%20health%20experts%20have%20sounded%20a%20warning%20over%20the%20increasing%20Covid-19%20cases%20in%20India%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20JN.1%20sub-variant%20of%20Omicron%20being%20detected%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2