res%20that%20make%20it%20usable%20for%20anything%20the%20winter%20has%20to%20offer.%20The%20powder%20skirt%20is%20a%20great%20feature%20for%20snow%20sports%20from%20snow%20tubing%20to%20more%20extreme%20sports%20like%20snowboarding.%20You'll%20also%20find%20fleece-lined%20hand%20warmer%20pockets%20on%20the%20outside%20and%20convenient%20media%20pockets%20on%20the%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFitting%20of%20the%20Mammoth%20name%2C%20this%20parka%20is%20slightly%20oversized%2C%20so%20I%20recommend%20going%20true%20to%20size.%20However%2C%20adjustable%20drawcords%20at%20the%20waist%20and%20Velcro%20cuffs%20allow%20you%20to%20adjust%20the%20fit%20to%20your%20liking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20high-end%3A%20Canada%20Goose%20Brockton%20Parka%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20building%20on%20a%20sidewalk%20wearing%20the%20Canada%20Goose%20Brockton%20Parka.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658323ffcefc010bea25a51d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmir%20Ismael%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDown%20fill%20power%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20750%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EExterior%20fabric%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Durable%20water-resistant%20polyester%20and%20cotton%20blend%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%203.5%20to%204.6%20lbs%2C%20depending%20on%20size%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHood%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Removable%2C%20adjustable%20toggle%20hood%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPockets%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%204%20exterior%20pockets%2C%203%20interior%20pockets%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESizing%20options%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20XS-XXL%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranty%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Lifetime%20warranty%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELonger%20back%20hem%20for%20increased%20coverage%2C%