old-weather%20designs%20have%20been%20adopted%20in%20fashion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInspired%20by%20the%20original%20Himalayan%20Down%20Parka%2C%20the%20HMLYN%20Down%20Parka%20bridges%20the%20gap%20between%20high-alpine%20gear%20and%20streetwear%20fashion.%20As%20a%20toned-down%20version%20of%20the%20original%2C%20the%20HMLYN%20Down%20Parka%20features%20the%20iconic%20retro%20look%20and%20feel%20of%20The%20North%20Face%20parkas%20with%20large%20down-filled%20baffles%20and%20bold%20color-blocking%2C%20while%20being%20more%20comfortable%20for%20daily%20wear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jacket%20features%20550-fill%20power%20down%2C%20durable%20water-resistant%20coating%2C%20adjustable%20cords%20on%20the%20hem%20and%20hood%2C%20and%20plenty%20of%20interior%20and%20exterior%20storage%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20HMLYN%20Down%20Parka%20is%20a%20great%20choice%20of%20men's%20winter%20coats%20for%20people%20who%20love%20the%20look%20of%20burly%20parkas%20like%20the%20original%20Himalayan%20Down%20Parka%2C%20but%20have%20no%20intentions%20of%20scaling%20any%20mountains.%20Not%20to%20mention%2C%20it's%20more%20affordable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20vegan%3A%20Frank%20and%20Oak%20Capital%20Parka%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%2C%20with%20a%20person%20wearing%20a%20parka%20next%20to%20a%20dog%20on%20the%20left%20and%20a%20person%20walking%20on%20the%20sidewalk%20on%20the%20right.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6579d02050edbc52a863c104%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESyd%20Hutnik%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDown%20fill%20power%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Vegan%20Primaloft%20ThermoPlume%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EExterior%20fabric%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Wind%20and%20water-resistant%20100%25%20recycled%20polyester%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%203.99%20lbs%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHood%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Attached%2C%20adjustable%20drawcord%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPockets%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202%20hand%20pockets%2C%201%20zippered%20sleeve%20pocket%2C%202%20interior%20pouches%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESizing%20options%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20XS-XXL%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranty%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20N%2FA%2C%2015%20days%20from%20the%20date%20your%20order%20is%20shipped%20to%20request%20a%20prepaid%20return%20shipping%20label%20online%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E100%25%20recycled%20and%20vegan%2C%20plenty%20of%20zippered%20compartments%20for%20storage%2C%20backpack-style%20straps%20for%20indoor%20convenience%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESleek%20and%20slim%20design%20doesn't%20have%20classic%20parka%20look%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Ffrank-and-oak-sustainable-outerwear-review%5C%22%3EFrank%20and%20Oak%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20brand%20known%20for%20crossing%20cruelty-free%20and%20recycled%20materials%20with%20high%20performance%2C%20finds%20a%20solid%20middle%20ground%20in%20between%20bulk%20and%20warmth%20with%20their%20Capital%20Parka.%20While%20the%20Parka%20definitely%20has%20an%20appropriate%20amount%20of%20bulk%20to%20keep%20you%20warm%2C%20and%20also%20the%20right%20length%20to%20cover%20your%20posterior%2C%20it's%20not%20overly%20heavy%20and%20when%20I'm%20wearing%20it%20I%20don't%20feel%20like%20I'm%20taking%20up%20more%20than%20my%20allotted%20space%20in%20a%20busy%20Subway%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20tested%20a%20previous%20version%20of%20this%20parka%20that%20boasted%2060%25%20recycled%20polyester%20and%2040%25%20regular%20polyester%2C%20the%20new%20iteration%20now%20has%20zero%20virgin%20polyester%20in%20addition%20to%20being%20completely%20vegan%20and%20cruelty-free.%20Instead%20of%20goose%20or%20duck%20feathers%20to%20fill%20the%20jacket%2C%20they%20utilize%20Primaloft%20ThermoPlume%20insulation%2C%20designed%20to%20keep%20you%20warm%20in%20temperatures%20as%20low%20as%2022%20below%20zero.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20jacket%20is%20windproof%20and%20waterproof%2C%20with%20a%20Hydrophobic%20shell%20and%20waterproofed%20sealed%20seams%2C%20and%20even%20waterproofed%20zipped%20pockets.%20I%20also%20appreciate%20the%20jersey%20sleeve%2C%20which%20helps%20keep%20your%20wrists%20protected%20on%20a%20windy%20day.%20What%20this%20all%20boils%20down%20to%20is%20that%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20compromise%20on%20performance%20to%20wear%20this%20coat%20that%20matches%20your%20sustainability%20and%20ethical%20guidelines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFunctionally%2C%20the%20coat%20checks%20off%20what%20most%20people%20who%20aren't%20wandering%20around%20in%20sub-freezing%20temperatures%20need%2C%20while%20also%20offering%20a%20sleek%20design%20with%20plenty%20of%20fun%20convenience%20features.%20My%20favorite%20features%20are%20the%20magnets%20that%20clasp%20the%20main%20zipper%20and%20exterior%20pockets%20closed%20because%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20buttoning%20or%20clasping%20anything%20to%20fully%20seal%20yourself%20from%20the%20cold.%20This%20is%20also%20especially%20helpful%20when%20you're%20wearing%20gloves%20or%20mittens.%20There's%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20interior%20pocket%20space%2C%20one%20side%20with%20three%20compartments%2C%20a%20zipper%20section%20on%20top%20of%20a%20velcro%20on%20top%20of%20a%20mesh%20pouch%2C%20and%20a%20singular%20velcro%20pouch%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20sneaky%20zipper%20pocket%20on%20the%20sleeve%20that%20is%20perfect%20for%20quick%20access%20items%20like%20a%20credit%20card%20or%20a%20pack%20of%20tissues%20plus%20another%20hidden%20pocket%20on%20the%20outside%20of%20the%20main%20zipper.%20The%20hood%20and%20waist%20can%20be%20tightened%20to%20your%20liking%2C%20and%20the%20jacket%20also%20comes%20with%20backpack%20straps%20attached%20to%20the%20interior.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%94%20%3Cstrong%3EDanny%20Bakst%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3ESenior%20Manager%2C%20Story%20Production%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20oversized%3A%20The%20North%20Face%20Coldworks%20Insulated%20Parka%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20wearing%20The%20North%20Face%20Coldworks%20jacket%20on%20a%20street.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65833043a79e5746976bb8f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmir%20Ismael%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDown%20fill%20power%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2050%2F50%20blend%20of%20synthetic%20and%20600-fill%20down%20insulation%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EExterior%20fabric%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20DryVent%20100%25%20recycled%20nylon%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20N%2FA%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHood%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Removable%20hood%20with%20adjustable%20drawcords%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPockets%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%202%20chest%20pockets%2C%202%20lower%20pockets%2C%202%20handwarmer%20pockets%2C%201%20media%20pocket%2C%20and%202%20interior%20mesh%20pockets%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESizing%20options%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20XS-XXL%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranty%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Lifetime%20warranty%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELots%20of%20pockets%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENo%20adjustable%20drawcords%20at%20waist%20or%20hem%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20something%20about%20an%20oversized%20parka%20that%20always%20wins%20me%20over.%20Not%20only%20is%20comfortable%20to%20wear%20a%20coat%20that's%20not%20tight%20and%20restrictive%2C%20but%20if%20you%20choose%20the%20right%20one%2C%20it'll%20look%20great%2C%20too.%20The%20North%20Face's%20Coldworks%20Insulated%20Parka%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best-looking%20and%20most%20useful%20choices%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20North%20Face%20is%20often%20known%20for%20its%20bright%20color-blocking%20(which%20I%20love%20too)%2C%20but%20it's%20refreshing%20to%20see%20some%20neutral%20colors%20like%20the%20Almond%20Butter%20I%20tested%20and%20the%20Coal%20Brown%20that's%20also%20available.%20Aside%20from%20the%20color%20options%2C%20the%20style%20is%20timeless.%20It%20features%20four%20large%20pockets%20at%20the%20chest%20and%20hips%20that%20are%20reminiscent%20of%20military%20field%20jackets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Coldworks%20Parka%20isn't%20the%20absolute%20warmest%20jacket%20in%20terms%20of%20a%20fill%20power%20rating%2C%20but%20it%20has%20excellent%20coverage%20to%20block%20out%20the%20cold%20with%20the%20below-the-waist%20fit%2C%20adjustable%20hood%2C%20and%20adjustable%20cuffs.%20Plus%2C%20the%20relaxed%20oversized%20fit%20allows%20you%20to%20adequately%20layer%20up%20underneath.%20I%20love%20to%20wear%20chunky%20sweaters%2C%20hoodies%2C%20and%20fleeces%20in%20the%20winter%2C%20didn't%20mind%20wearing%20another%20layer%20for%20added%20warmth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20not%20having%20the%20highest%20fill%20power%20rating%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20hesitate%20to%20wear%20it%20in%20the%20snow.%20It's%20made%20using%20The%20North%20Face's%20proprietary%20DryVent%20material%2C%20so%20it's%20waterproof%20and%20breathable%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20disappointment%20I%20had%20with%20this%20parka%20was%20the%20lack%20of%20an%20adjustable%20draw%20cord%20at%20the%20hem.%20As%20much%20as%20I%20like%20the%20style%2C%20this%20parka%20fits%20me%20just%20a%20bit%20%3Cem%3Etoo%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebig%20in%20a%20size%20medium.%20If%20you're%20in%20between%20sizes%20like%20I%20am%2C%20I%20recommend%20choosing%20the%20smaller%20size%20because%20you'll%20still%20have%20plenty%20of%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20parkas%20for%20men%20FAQs%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20brands%20sustainably%20use%20down%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sustainability%20and%20ethics%20surrounding%20down%20and%20fur%20are%20inherently%20points%20of%20contention.%20The%20animal%20welfare%20of%20waterfowl%20is%20slightly%20more%20clear-cut%20and%20traceable%3A%20Many%20of%20the%20brands%20in%20our%20guide%2C%20including%20Fjallraven%20and%20Triple%20F.A.T.%20Goose%2C%20put%20their%20down%20through%20rigorous%20testing%20to%20identify%20whether%20or%20not%20the%20down%20was%20plucked%20from%20live%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETriple%20F.A.T.%20Goose%20puts%20its%20down%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idfl.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternational%20Down%20and%20Feather%20Testing%20Laboratory%20(IDFL)%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20meet%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fresponsibledown.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F07%2FTE-Responsible-Down-Standard-2.0-opt.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EResponsible%20Down%20Standard%20(RDS)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Then%20there's%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nsf.org%2Fnewsroom_pdf%2Fsu_traceble_down_infopaper.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlobal%20Traceable%20Down%20Standard%20(Global%20TDS)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20certified%20by%20the%20NSF%20and%20slightly%20more%20rigorous%20in%20requiring%20parent%20farm%20certification.%20That%20means%20that%20whatever%20farm%20an%20egg%20or%20a%20hatchling%20came%20from%20must%20be%20certified%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtherwise%2C%20the%20RDS%20and%20Global%20TDS%20are%20almost%20identical%2C%20and%20both%20essentially%20uphold%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aspca.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fupload%2Fimages%2Faspca_asv_five_freedoms_final1.ashx_.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFive%20Freedoms%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20ducks%20and%20geese%20whose%20feathers%20and%20down%20are%20collected%20are%20not%20force-fed%2C%20live-plucked%2C%20malnourished%2C%20or%20transported%20from%20farm%20to%20farm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20brands%20still%20use%20real%20fur%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20do%2C%20yes.%20Fur%20can%20come%20from%20animals%20that%20have%20been%20farmed%20(as%20is%20often%20the%20case%20with%20foxes%20and%20minks)%2C%20or%20it%20can%20come%20from%20wild%20animals.%20Coyote%20fur%2C%20which%20is%20usually%20what%20you'll%20see%20adorning%20parkas%2C%20is%20generally%20trapped%20or%20hunted.%20A%20lot%20of%20brands%20source%20coyote%20fur%20from%20places%20where%20they're%20deemed%20to%20be%20a%20problem%20species%2C%20either%20by%20way%20of%20overpopulation%2C%20mange%2C%20or%20invasiveness.%20Blue%20fox%20is%20the%20most%20common%20type%20of%20fox%20fur%20used%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20is%20often%20sourced%20from%20farms%20certified%20by%20Nordic%20fur%20trading%20companies%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sagafurs.com%2Fsustainability%2Fcertification%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESaga%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20brands%20disclose%20their%20own%20use%20of%20fur%2C%20a%20general%20practice%20is%20to%20list%20their%20compliance%20and%20cooperation%20with%20game%20trapping%20laws%20and%20standards%20set%20forth%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffur.ca%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2FAIHTS-Copy-of-Agreement.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAgreement%20on%20International%20Humane%20Trapping%20Standards%20(AIHTS)%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Canada%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fishwildlife.org%2Fafwa-inspires%2Ffurbearer-management%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBest%20Management%20Practices%20(BMP)%3C%2Fa%3E%20standards%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFur%20does%20indeed%20have%20moisture-wicking%20properties%20and%20warmth%20that%20no%20synthetic%20material%20can%20match.%20But%20we%20see%20it%20being%20phased%20out%20by%20more%20and%20more%20brands%2C%20as%20public%20opinion%20has%20generally%20shifted%20towards%20%26quot%3Bcruelty%20free%26quot%3B%20alternatives.%20For%20example%2C%20Triple%20F.A.T.%20Goose%20stopped%20producing%20new%20fur%20based%20products%20as%20of%202021.%20Canada%20Goose%20still%20offers%20fur%20trimmed%20parkas%2C%20but%20announced%20they%20stopped%20manufacturing%20with%20fur%20in%20late%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-mens-parka%5C%22%3EInsider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703111925000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65831a7aa79e5746976ba6cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-mens-parka%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parkas%20are%20heavy-duty%20winter%20coats%20that%20keep%20you%20warm%20in%20extreme%20cold.%20Here%20are%20the%20best%20we've%20tested%20from%20brands%20like%20The%20North%20Face%20and%20Canada%20Goose.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aismael%40insider.com%20(Amir%20Ismael)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-mens-parka%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%202023%20music%20scene%20is%202013%20all%20over%20again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22beyonc%C3%A9%20mine%20music%20video%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65807332a79e5746976a7e2a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221602%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBeyonc%C3%A9%20in%20%26quot%3BMine%26quot%3B%20(2013).%3Cp%3EBeyonc%C3%A9%2FYouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20pop-music%20trends%20of%202023%20bear%20a%20striking%20resemblance%20to%202013%2C%20both%20sonically%20and%20aesthetically.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EToday%2C%20Tumblr-era%20artists%20like%20The%201975%20and%20Lana%20Del%20Rey%20are%20as%20popular%20as%20ever.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMoreover%2C%20we've%20seen%20a%20revival%20of%202013%20lyrical%20themes%2C%20especially%20a%20suspicion%20of%20modernity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20this%20time%20last%20December%2C%20just%20as%20the%20winter%20chill%20began%20to%20creep%20in%2C%20I%20made%20a%20playlist%20titled%20%26quot%3BI'm%2018%20years%20old%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20nostalgia%20was%20triggered%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbest-albums-this-year-ranked-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethen-recent%20releases%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20The%201975's%20%26quot%3BBeing%20Funny%20in%20a%20Foreign%20Language%26quot%3B%20and%20Arctic%20Monkeys'%20%26quot%3BThe%20Car.%26quot%3B%20Those%20bands%20delivered%20two%20formative%20albums%20of%20my%20adolescence%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%201975%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAM%2C%26quot%3B%20both%20released%20in%20September%202013%2C%20the%20same%20month%20I%20began%20my%20freshman%20year%20of%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20made%20the%20playlist%2C%20I%20was%20working%20off%20a%20hunch.%20But%20something%20in%20the%20air%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20more%20accurately%2C%20something%20on%20my%20phone%20screen%20%E2%80%94%20carried%20the%20peculiar%20suspense%20of%20homecoming.%20My%20indie-sleaze%20spidey%20senses%2C%20honed%20over%20many%20years%20as%20an%20active%20Tumblr%20user%2C%20were%20tingling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20%E2%80%94%20a%20full%20decade%20after%20I%20reblogged%20a%20photo%20of%20Matty%20Healy%20for%20the%20first%20time%20%E2%80%94%20that%20faint%20whisper%20of%20reprise%20seemed%20to%20solidify.%20From%20a%20pop-music%20lover's%20perspective%2C%202023%20looks%20a%20lot%20like%20a%202013%20doppelg%C3%A4nger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22matty%20healy%20the%201975%20then%20and%20now%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658078c2a79e5746976a81fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%201975%20frontman%20Matty%20Healy%20in%202013%20and%202023.%3Cp%3EJoseph%20Okpako%2FRob%20Ball%2FWireImage%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20often%20said%20that%20trends%20are%20cyclical%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fthe-goods%2F2020%2F5%2F7%2F21247938%2Ftumblr-aesthetic-2014-nostalgia-tiktok-indie-pop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eso%20this%20isn't%20exactly%20a%20revelation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20New%20generations%20make%20old%20fads%20cool%20again.%20Low-rise%20jeans%20and%20ballet%20flats%20are%20back%2C%20somehow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20hard%20to%20deny%20the%20parallel%20appeal%20of%20these%20two%20sister%20years%20%E2%80%94%20or%20the%20sheer%20volume%20of%20mirror%20images%20that%20have%20dominated%20my%20feeds%20for%20the%20past%2012%20months%2C%20familiar%20to%20anyone%20who%20once%20considered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inc.com%2Fmagazine%2F201106%2Fthe-way-i-work-david-karp-of-tumblr.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavid%20Karp%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20personal%20hero.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%201975's%20current%20tour%2C%20aptly%20titled%20%26quot%3BStill%E2%80%A6%20At%20Their%20Very%20Best%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20extended%20into%202024%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rollingstone.co.uk%2Fmusic%2Flive-reviews%2Fthe-1975-live-in-brighton-a-game-changing-arena-show-for-the-ages-25605%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eigniting%20a%20surge%20of%20critical%20praise%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20an%20explosion%20of%20interest%20on%20TikTok.%20(I%20know%20it's%20been%20a%20long%20year%2C%20but%20don't%20tell%20me%20you've%20already%20forgotten%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40dimariacountmein%2Fvideo%2F7195015343419510059%3Fis_from_webapp%3D1%26sender_device%3Dpc%26web_id%3D7292150377570190879%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bdon't%20like%20menthols%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20phase.)%20The%20elusive%20Frank%20Ocean%2C%20who%20once%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpitchfork.com%2Ffeatures%2Farticle%2F2010s-how-tumblr-culture-legitimized-queer-fandom-frank-ocean-troye-sivan-one-direction%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eused%20Tumblr%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20create%20his%20mythology%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fcoachella-frank-ocean-performance-review-disappointing-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheadlined%20Coachella%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April.%20Lana%20Del%20Rey's%20latest%20offering%20%26quot%3BDid%20You%20Know%20That%20There's%20a%20Tunnel%20Under%20Ocean%20Blvd%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20continues%20to%20paint%20the%20singer%20as%20a%20tragic%20Americana%20icon%2C%20is%20a%20frontrunner%20for%20album%20of%20the%20year%20at%20the%20upcoming%20Grammy%20Awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lana%20del%20rey%20music%20videos%20then%20and%20now%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65807938a79e5746976a8225%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELana%20Del%20Rey%20in%20%26quot%3BYoung%20and%20Beautiful%26quot%3B%20(2013)%20and%20%26quot%3BCandy%20Necklace%26quot%3B%20(2023).%3Cp%3ELana%20Del%20Rey%2FYouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20true%20that%20Ocean%20and%20Del%20Rey%20never%20really%20went%20out%20of%20style.%20But%20the%202013%20revival%20goes%20deeper%20than%20certain%20artists%20being%20as%20popular%20as%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20artists%20who%20released%20music%20that%20year%20were%20grappling%20with%20a%20strange%2C%20transitional%20vibe.%20Words%20like%20%26quot%3Bselfie%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bemoji%26quot%3B%20had%20just%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsfeed.time.com%2F2013%2F08%2F28%2Fdictionary-adds-badassery-selfie-and-twerk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_bl