gcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Kiani%20started%20the%20company%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20improving%20pulse%20oxomiters%2C%20the%20CEO%20worked%207%20days%20a%20week%20and%20only%20took%20two-four%20day%20weekends%20for%20seven%20years%2C%20he%20said%20during%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6v3dro6sauI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2013%20commencement%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Chapman%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20led%20the%20development%20of%20Masimo's%20Signal%20Extraction%20Technology%2C%20a%20pulse%20oximeter%20that%20the%20company%20claims%20can%20accurately%20measure%20blood%20oxygen%20levels%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20patient%20is%20in%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMasimo%20went%20public%20in%202007%20and%20now%20has%20a%20market%20cap%20of%20about%20%246%20billion.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22ceo%20of%20masimo%20joe%20kiani%20with%20his%20arms%20wide%20open%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65834a88a79e5746976bd500%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKiani's%20company%20had%20a%20market%20cap%20of%20about%20%246%20billion%20as%20of%20December%2020th.%3Cp%3EMANJUNATH%20KIRAN%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMasimo%20is%20now%20behind%20a%20slate%20of%20non-invasive%20patient%20monitoring%20devices%20that%20aim%20to%20improve%20patient%20safety%20and%20reduce%20the%20cost%20of%20care.%20Under%20Kiani's%20leadership%2C%20Masimo's%20devices%20were%20adopted%20by%20hospitals%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Kiani%20isn't%20leading%20Masimo%2C%20he%20focuses%20his%20efforts%20on%20healthcare%20advocacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKiani%20has%20been%20advocating%20for%20improving%20patient%20safety%20outcomes%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22kiani%20speaking%20at%20the%20patie