ns%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20donating%205%25%20of%20its%20net%20profits%20to%20a%20variety%20of%20reputable%20foundations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20natural%20without%20baking%20soda%3A%20Dr.%20Squatch%20Deodorant%3Cp%3EDr.%20Squatch%20describes%20itself%20as%20a%20natural%2C%20high-performance%20personal%20care%20brand%20specifically%20for%20men.%20Free%20of%20any%20harmful%20ingredients%2C%20all%20of%20its%20products%20are%2098-100%25%20natural%20and%20use%20naturally%20derived%20fragrances%20that%20men%20will%20love.%20And%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.drsquatch.com%2Fpages%2Fglossary%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eingredients%20glossary%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20fully%20describes%20the%20origins%20and%20purpose%20of%20each%20ingredient%2C%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20most%20transparent%20grooming%20brands%20I've%20come%20across.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20deodorizing%20and%20sweat-absorbing%20ingredients%20in%20Dr.%20Squatch's%20deodorants%20are%20charcoal%20powder%2C%20arrowroot%20powder%2C%20and%20magnesium.%C2%A0%20A%20host%20of%20other%20natural%20ingredients%20like%20coconut%20oil%2C%20beeswax%2C%20and%20essential%20oils%20are%20used%20for%20moisture%20and%20scent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20worried%20about%20an%20all-natural%20deodorant%20that%20doesn't%20deliver%20in%20the%20scent%20department%2C%20Dr.%20Squatch%20won't%20let%20you%20down.%20Some%20of%20my%20favorite%20scents%20are%20Wood%20Barrel%20Bourbon%2C%20Rainforest%20Rapids%2C%20and%20Fresh%20Fall%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20last%20for%20hours%20on%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20its%20distinctly%20masculine%20scents%2C%20Dr.%20Squatch's%20products%20are%20formulated%20specifically%20for%20men%20by%20including%20additional%20ingredients%20that%20can%20be%20potentially%20beneficial%20to%20men's%20health%2C%20such%20as%20saw%20palmetto%2C%20ginseng%2C%20and%20valerian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20natural%20with%20baking%20soda%3A%20American%20Provenance%3Cp%3EFounded%20by%20Kyle%20LaFond%2C%20a%20former%20middle%20school%20science%20teacher%2C%20American%20Provenance%20is%20a%20natural%20care%20essentials%20brand.%20All%20of%20the%20deodorants%20are%20hand-mixed%2C%20hand-poured%2C%20and%20made%20in%20small%20batches%20here%20in%20the%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20brand%20uses%20what%20it%20calls%20%26quot%3Bbetter-for-you%20ingredients%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20products.%20The%20deodorant%20uses%20coconut%20oil%20for%20its%20antibacterial%20properties%2C%20baking%20soda%20to%20deodorize%2C%20arrowroot%20to%20absorb%20sweat%20and%20bodily%20oils%2C%20and%20beeswax%20and%20shea%20butter%20to%20hydrate%20and%20soothe%20the%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20few%20scents%20I've%20used%2C%20none%20of%20them%20smell%20particularly%20masculine%20or%20feminine%2C%20so%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20best%20deodorant%20choices%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20unisex%20deodorant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20sensitive%20skin%3A%20Bevel%3Cp%3EBevel%20is%20a%20Black-owned%20grooming%20brand%20that%20makes%20affordable%20essentials%20for%20people%20of%20color.%20With%20everything%20from%20safety%20razors%20that%20prevent%20ingrown%20hairs%20to%20exfoliating%20body%20washes%2C%20one%20of%20Bevel's%20top%20priorities%20is%20to%20promote%20healthy%20skin%20while%20grooming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Aluminium-Free%20Deodorant%20is%20specifically%20designed%20to%20penetrate%20coarse%20and%20curly%20hair%2C%20so%20it%20actually%20gets%20to%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20skin%20to%20do%20its%20job.%20The%20formula%20also%20includes%20ingredients%20like%20coconut%20oil%2C%20and%20shea%20butter%20to%20keep%20skin%20hydrated%20and%20moisturized.%20It%20goes%20on%20smooth%20and%20clear%2C%20doesn't%20clump%20up%2C%20and%20provides%2048-hour%20odor%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20won't%20get%20to%20choose%20between%20a%20variety%20of%20scents%20for%20the%20deodorant%2C%20but%20it%20has%20a%20fresh%20scent%20most%20people%20will%20enjoy%20wearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20budget%3A%20Harry's%20Deodorant%20and%20Antiperspirant%3Cp%3EHarry's%20was%20originally%20founded%20in%202013%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20expensive%20store-bought%20disposable%20razors.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20the%20brand%20has%20expanded%20to%20become%20a%20total%20men's%20grooming%20brand%2C%20selling%20everything%20from%20shaving%20products%20to%20skincare%20%E2%80%94%20and%20its%20latest%20addition%20is%20deodorant%2C%20antiperspirant%2C%20and%20extra-strength%20antiperspirant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20type%20is%20designed%20to%20provide%2048-hour%20odor%20protection.%20The%20deodorant%20is%20aluminum-free%2C%20while%20the%20antiperspirants%20use%20aluminum%20to%20prevent%20sweating.%20Regardless%20of%20which%20type%20you%20choose%2C%20Harry's%20deodorants%20and%20antiperspirants%20are%20affordably%20priced%20at%20%245.50.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deodorants%20and%20antiperspirants%20come%20in%20of%20a%20variety%20of%20scents%2C%20many%20of%20which%20have%20an%20outdoorsy%20natural%20smell.%20If%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20fresh%20scent%20that's%20closer%20to%20body%20wash%20or%20cologne%2C%20this%20might%20not%20be%20the%20one%20for%20you.%20However%2C%20each%20name%20clearly%20describes%20the%20scent%20profile%2C%20so%20it's%20easy%20to%20choose%20one%20you'll%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20moisturizing%3A%20Dove%20Men%2BCare%3Cp%3EDeodorant%20is%20used%20to%20keep%20body%20odor%20under%20control%2C%20but%20harsh%20ingredients%20can%20often%20have%20a%20negative%20effect%20on%20your%20underarm%20skin.%20If%20you're%20dealing%20with%20dry%2C%20peeling%2C%20or%20itchy%20skin%20on%20your%20underarms%2C%20there's%20a%20good%20chance%20that%20your%20skin%20doesn't%20agree%20with%20your%20current%20deodorant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dove.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fmen-care%2Fdeodorant.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDove%20Men%2BCare%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20developed%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20men%2C%20while%20nourishing%20skin.%20Of%20the%20many%20deodorant%20choices%20from%20Dove%20Men%2BCare%2C%20I%20most%20recommend%20the%20Extra%20Fresh%20Deodorant%20Stick.%20This%20formula%20is%20aluminum-free%20and%20is%20made%20with%20%C2%BC%20moisturizing%20cream%2C%20so%20it%20won't%20irritate%20your%20skin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20said%20to%20have%2072-hour%20odor%20protection%2C%20and%20while%20I've%20never%20gone%20that%20long%20without%20showering%20and%20re-applying%20deodorant%2C%20it%20does%20an%20excellent%20job%20at%20lasting%20all%20day.%20The%20%26quot%3Bextra%20fresh%26quot%3B%20scent%20is%20a%20blend%20of%20bergamot%2C%20lavender%2C%20and%20sandalwood%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20which%20suppress%20odor%20and%20keep%20you%20smelling%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20high-end%3A%20Jack%20Black%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202000%2C%20when%20the%20grooming%20and%20beauty%20industry%20was%20primarily%20saturated%20with%20products%20for%20women%2C%20Jack%20Black%20was%20one%20of%20earliest%20brands%20to%20create%20high-quality%20grooming%20essentials%20using%20natural%20ingredients%20for%20men.%20While%20the%20market%20has%20plenty%20of%20natural%20or%20clean%20brands%20for%20men%2C%20Jack%20Black%20is%20still%20one%20of%20the%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJack%20Black's%20Pit%20Boss%20antiperspirant%20is%20free%20of%20parabens%20and%20sulfates%20and%20uses%20natural%20ingredients%20like%20vitamin%20E%2C%20aloe%20leaf%20juice%2C%20castor%20oil%2C%20and%20sunflower%20seed%20oil%20to%20protect%20and%20moisturize%20the%20skin.%20As%20an%20antiperspirant%2C%20it%20uses%20aluminum%20to%20reduce%20underarm%20wetness%20and%20control%20sweat.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20won't%20get%20to%20choose%20between%20a%20variety%20of%20scents%20with%20Jack%20Black%20Pit%20Boss%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20mind%20because%20it%20has%20one%20of%20the%20freshest%20scents%20I've%20tried%20and%20lasts