3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20benefit%20to%20shopping%20for%20deodorant%20at%20Old%20Spice%20is%20variety.%20Whether%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20strong%20antiperspirant%20with%20aluminum%2C%20an%20aluminum-free%20deodorant%2C%20a%20spray-on%2C%20or%20a%20natural%20formula%20from%20the%20Gentlemen's%20Blend%20collection%2C%20the%20brand%20has%20something%20to%20meet%20every%20man's%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20aluminum-free%20stick%20deodorant%20is%20great%20for%20everyday%20use%2C%20I%20really%20enjoyed%20using%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-62324-20%26h%3D48e83a08612d560f792cc90535df169ad19d1e33f29eb6ce3ea1847b6f5d8f85%26postID%3D6580656b8d7dad6fbf2c41e7%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fbest-mens-deodorant-antiperspirant%26site%3Din%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.target.com%252Fp%252Fold-spice-men-39-s-antiperspirant-38-deodorant-invisible-dry-spray-stronger-swagger-4-3-oz%252F-%252FA-83723461%2523lnk%253Dsametab%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDry%20Spray%20antiperspirant%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20before%20workouts.%20It%20goes%20on%20dry%2C%20doesn't%20stain%20clothes%2C%20and%20has%20a%20long%20lasting%20scent.%20Regardless%20of%20what%20type%20of%20deodorant%20or%20antiperspirant%20you%20choose%2C%20they're%20all%20affordably%20priced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFAQs%3Ch2%3EWhat's%20the%20difference%20between%20deodorant%20and%20antiperspirant%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20difference%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdeodorant-vs-antiperspirant%5C%22%3Edeodorant%20and%20antiperspirant%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20that%20deodorants%20don't%20control%20the%20amount%20you%20sweat%20%E2%80%94%20they%20only%20prevent%20the%20smell%20of%20body%20odor.%20Antiperspirants%20instead%20block%20sweat%20glands%20using%20aluminum%20to%20prevent%20hyperhidrosis%20(AKA%3A%20excessive%20sweating)%2C%20and%20some%20formulas%20h