%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe-Vibe%20accomplished%20something%20incredibly%20rare%20with%20its%20Chorus%20vibrator%3A%20It%20created%20a%20wearable%20toy%20that%20doesn't%20get%20in%20the%20way%20during%20sex.%20Its%20flexible%20design%20fits%20virtually%20anybody%2C%20and%20its%20nearly-flat%20inner%20arm%20ensures%20that%20a%20penis%20won't%20get%20snagged%20on%20it%20mid-thrust.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20arms%20vibrate%20to%20four%20speeds%20and%20six%20patterns%2C%20although%20the%20outer%20arm%20has%20decidedly%20more%20oomph%20than%20the%20inner%20arm.%20Still%2C%20this%20little%20toy%20buzzes%20against%20your%20G-spot%2C%20your%20clitoris%2C%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20your%20partner's%20penis%2C%20giving%20them%20a%20pleasurable%20sensation%20as%20they%20thrust.%20And%20those%20vibrations%20are%20the%20deep%2C%20rumbly%20kind%20instead%20of%20the%20topical%20buzzing%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20vibrators%20have%2C%20which%20is%20great%20for%20penetrative%20use.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20toy%20also%20has%20something%20called%20Touch-Sense%2C%20which%20is%20meant%20to%20change%20the%20speed%20of%20the%20vibrations%20depending%20on%20your%20movement.%20For%20the%20life%20of%20me%2C%20I%20just%20couldn't%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20make%20this%20work%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20trickier%20components%20of%20the%20Chorus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20where%20this%20toy%20shines%20is%20with%20its%20squeeze%20remote.%20While%20the%20controller%20does%20have%20up%20and%20down%20arrows%2C%20you%20can%20also%20squeeze%20and%20hold%20the%20outer%2C%20squishy%20part.%20This%20increases%20the%20speed%20of%20the%20vibration%20for%20as%20long%20as%20you're%20holding%20it%2C%20which%20I%20found%20to%20be%20a%20highly%20enjoyable%20alternative%20to%20fumbling%20with%20specific%20controls%20while%20in%20use.%20The%20vibrator%20also%20connects%20to%20We-Vibe's%20app%20which%2C%20when%20connected%20to%20WiFi%2C%20can%20control%20your%20vibrators%20from%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20the%20bells%20and%20whistles%2C%20the%20Chorus%20is%20just%20a%20great%20vibrator.%20It's%20waterproof%2C%20easy%20to%20clean%2C%20and%20rechargeable.%20I%20even%20enjoy%20it%20sans%20a%20partner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20finger%3A%20Dame%20Fin%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Dame%20Fin%20vibrator.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f19db4a19182454744ab303%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EDame%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEasy%20to%20pull%20on%20and%20off%2C%20removable%20tether%2C%20and%20strong%2C%20whisper-quiet%20vibrations%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20pointy%20end%20can%20be%20intense%2C%20so%20you%20may%20need%20to%20switch%20between%20that%20and%20the%20squishy%20side%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinger%20vibrators%20of%20the%20past%20used%20to%20be%20dinky%20and%20weak%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20Dame%20Fin%20is%20so%20revolutionary.%20It's%20versatile%20with%20strong%20vibrations%20and%20an%20ergonomic%20design.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20finger%20tether%20is%20removable%2C%20so%20you%20can%20slip%20it%20on%20and%20off%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20you%20use%20it.%20And%20you%20can%20wear%20it%20with%20the%20vibrator%20tip%20pointing%20up%20or%20down.%20And%20even%20when%20the%20tether%20is%20off%2C%20the%20vibe%20stays%20put%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20squishy%20finger%20notch%20that%20doesn't%20vibrate%20your%20fingers%20numb.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dame%20Fin%20has%20three%20different%20vibration%20speeds%2C%20with%20the%20highest%20speed%20being%20super%20powerful.%20I%20was%20shocked%20by%20how%20rumbly%20it%20was%20%E2%80%94%20it%20stimulated%20just%20as%20well%20as%20some%20of%20my%20larger%20vibes.%20And%20it's%20slim%20enough%20that%20you%20can%20slip%20it%20between%20you%20and%20your%20partner%20during%20sex.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fin's%20tether%20also%20easily%20slips%20off%20even%20if%20you're%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20using%20it%2C%20and%20the%20buzzing%20is%20quiet%20enough%20that%20it%20won't%20distract%20you%20(or%20wake%20the%20neighbors).%20It's%20water-resistant%2C%20too%2C%20and%20made%20of%20medical-grade%20silicone%2C%20making%20it%20great%20for%20anyone%20with%20sensitive%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20pointy%20side%20can%20be%20a%20little%20intense%20with%20its%20targeted%20vibrations%2C%20though.%20I%20found%20myself%20feeling%20over-sensitive%20and%20needing%20a%20break%20after%20a%20few%20minutes%20of%20extended%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20suction%3A%20Satisfyer%20Pro%202%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Satisfyer%20Pro.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f19dc04f34d054a4c6d2433%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESatisfyer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E11%20vibration%20modes%2C%20no%20direct%20contact%20with%20your%20clitoris%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20little%20noisier%20before%20it%20creates%20its%20seal%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Satisfyer%20Pro%202%20delivers%20a%20completely%20different%20sensation%20to%20standard%20vibrators%20in%20that%20it%20provides%20suction.%20It's%20ideal%20for%20people%20who%20love%20the%20feel%20of%20oral%20sex%20over%20the%20sometimes-intense%20buzzing%20of%20a%20traditional%20bullet%20vibe.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Satisfyer%20Pro%202%20uses%20a%20pulsing%20sensation%20that%20provides%20the%20feel%20of%20sucking%20against%20your%20clitoris.%20It%20has%20a%20little%20notch%20that%20slips%20over%20your%20clitoris%20and%20creates%20a%20bit%20of%20suction%2C%20giving%20you%20a%20true-to-life%20mouth%20feeling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20favorite%20part%20about%20the%20Satisfyer%20Pro%202%20is%20the%20shape%20%E2%80%94%20it%20almost%20looks%20like%20a%20hairbrush%20with%20a%20small%20nose%20on%20the%20top.%20The%20only%20part%20that%20vibrates%20is%20that%20little%20nose%2C%20so%20your%20wrist%20or%20hands%20don't%20feel%20numb%20from%20the%20vibrations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Satisfyer%20Pro%202%20has%2011%20different%20speeds%20and%20an%20easy-to-access%20control%20panel%20on%20the%20handle%2C%20so%20it's%20easy%20to%20start%20slow%20and%20cycle%20up%20into%20the%20more%20intense%20settings%20as%20you%20play.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20since%20there's%20no%20direct%20contact%20with%20your%20clitoris%20like%20other%20vibrators%2C%20you%20don't%20get%20over-sensitive%2C%20which%20is%20great%20if%20you're%20someone%20who%20likes%20longer%20sessions.%20It's%20even%20slim%20enough%20to%20slip%20between%20you%20and%20your%20partner%20during%20sex%20for%20some%20super%20intense%20stimulation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Satisfyer%20Pro%202%20is%20waterproof%20and%20easy%20to%20clean%2C%20though%20it%20is%20a%20bit%20loud%20before%20it%20creates%20a%20suction%2C%20so%20you%20may%20want%20to%20use%20this%20toy%20under%20some%20covers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20bullet%3A%20Tenga%20Iroha%20Temari%20KAZE%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Tenga%20Iroha%20Temari%20Kaze.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f19dc823f737064d16dcd3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ETenga%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E11%20vibration%20modes%2C%20no%20direct%20contact%20with%20your%20clitoris%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20little%20noisier%20before%20it%20creates%20its%20seal%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rarely%20use%20bullet%20vibrators%20for%20one%20specific%20reason%3A%20Their%20entire%20bodies%20tend%20to%20buzz%2C%20which%20can%20be%20painful%20on%20my%20hands%20and%20wrist.%20So%2C%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20when%20I%20used%20the%20Tenga%20Iroha%20Temari%20Kaze.%20It's%20a%20bullet%20vibrator%20that's%20shaped%20like%20an%20egg%20in%20an%20egg%20dish.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20design%20isn't%20just%20cute%20as%20the%20way%20the%20egg%20floats%20in%20the%20dish%20makes%20it%20so%20the%20egg%20is%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20vibrates.%20That%20means%20the%20outer%20dish%20doesn't%20buzz%2C%20which%20is%20great%20considering%20that's%20the%20place%20where%20you%20hold%20the%20vibrator%20and%20control%20the%20buzzing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tenga%20Iroha%20provides%20four%20speeds%20and%20two%20patterns%2C%20and%20it%20is%20hands-down%20the%20quietest%20vibrator%20in%20our%20guide.%20It's%20not%20as%20powerful%20as%20any%20of%20the%20other%20vibrators%2C%20although%20bullets%20rarely%20are.%20Its%20rounded%20tip%20also%20feels%20great%20against%20your%20clitoris.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20comes%20with%20a%20carrying%20case%2C%20too%2C%20which%20is%20a%20small%20dome%20cover%20that%20pops%20right%20on%20top%20of%20the%20egg%20dish.%20I%20love%20this%20because%20it%20means%20that%20I%20can%20keep%20the%20vibrator%20out%20while%20it's%20charging%20and%20no%20one%20will%20be%20the%20wiser.%20It's%20so%20well-designed%20that%20you%20might%20want%20to%20keep%20it%20out%20on%20your%20nightstand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20small%20nitpick%20would%20be%20that%20the%20Tenga%20was%20a%20little%20tough%20to%20clean%20since%20the%20silicone%20around%20the%20egg%20puckers%20a%20bit.%20I%20found%20myself%20having%20to%20get%20in%20there%20with%20a%20Q-tip%20to%20ensure%20that%20everything%20was%20fully%20clean%20%E2%80%94%20although%2C%20I%20will%20admit%20I'm%20a%20little%20obsessive%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20toy%20cleanliness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20G-spot%3A%20LELO%20Gigi%202%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Lelo%20vibrator.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5f19de3ff34d054cdf3088e3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESmaller%20than%20other%20internal%20vibrators%2C%20with%20a%20tip%20that%20feels%20good%20on%20your%20G-spot%20%3Cem%3Eand%20%3C%2Fem%3Eyour%20clit%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETakes%20two%20hours%20to%20fully%20charge%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beauty%20of%20the%20LELO%20Gigi%202%20is%20in%20its%20ergonomic%20shape.%20It%20has%20an%20oversized%2C%20flat%20tip%20that%20sits%20snugly%20against%20your%20G-spot%2C%20and%20unlike%20other%20internal%20vibrators%2C%20this%20one%20isn't%20so%20big%20that%20you'll%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20getting%20it%20in%20or%20out.%20If%20using%20lube%2C%20I%20suggest%20a%20water-based%20lubricant%20to%20ensure%20everything%20slips%20in%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20eight%20different%20vibration%20settings%20that%20you%20can%20cycle%20through%20via%20the%20controls%20on%20the%20handle.%20They're%20somewhat%20small%2C%20so%20I%20found%20myself%20fumbling%20with%20them%20a%20bit%20in%20the%20beginning.%20But%20once%20I%20knew%20where%20the%20buttons%20were%2C%20this%20issue%20was%20easily%20corrected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20LELO%20Gigi%202%20is%20made%20of%20super-smooth%20silicone%20and%20is%20completely%20waterproof%20(up%20to%20one%20meter).%20It%20does%20take%20a%20while%20to%20fully%20charge%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0roughly%20two%20hours%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0but%20it%20holds%20its%20charge%20for%20that%20long%2C%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20though%20this%20vibrator's%20tip%20is%20designed%20for%20your%20G-spot%2C%20it%20feels%20great%20against%20your%20clitoris%2C%20too.%20This%20is%20especially%20true%20if%20you're%20someone%20who%20loves%20direct%20stimulation.%20The%20vibrations%20also%20feel%20great%20elsewhere%20on%20your%20body%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20your%20nipples%20or%20your%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20I%20test%20vibrators%3Cp%3EWorking%20out%20which%20vibrators%20are%20best%20is%20fun%2C%20of%20course%2C%20but%20it%20also%20involves%20rigorous%20testing.%20It's%20not%20just%20about%20whether%20or%20not%20a%20vibe%20will%20get%20you%20off%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20stimulate%20yourself%20enough%20and%20you're%20all%20but%20guaranteed%20to%20get%20some%20kind%20of%20orgasm%20out%20of%20the%20deal.%20There%20are%20certain%20boxes%20a%20vibrator%20needs%20to%20check%20and%20while%20I%20looked%20into%20those%20myself%2C%20I%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20sexologists%20and%20sex%20educators%20for%20input.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20main%20criteria%20I%20looked%20for%20while%20testing%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELoudness%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIf%20you%20don't%20live%20alone%2C%20how%20quiet%20a%20vibrator%20is%20can%20be%20a%20major%20selling%20point.%20The%20quieter%2C%20the%20better.%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20decibel%20reader%2C%20so%20I%20chose%20a%20test%20that%20was%20a%20little%20more%20true-to-life.%20To%20ensure%20that%20all%20of%20our%20vibrators%20passed%20the%20shh-test%2C%20I%20listened%20to%20them%20in%20two%20ways%3A%20Under%20a%20blanket%2C%20and%20then%20on%20top%20of%20a%20blanket%20and%20behind%20a%20door.%20Scientific%3F%20No.%20But%20trust%20me%20%E2%80%94%20you%20want%20something%20that%20you%20can't%20hear%20through%20a%20door.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiscreetness%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EGone%20are%20the%20days%20of%20huge%2C%20penis-shaped%20vibrators.%20The%20best%20vibrators%20are%20discreet%2C%20with%20slim%20silhouettes%20you%20can%20easily%20stash.%20In%20my%20testing%2C%20vibes%20also%20got%20extra%20points%20for%20coming%20with%20a%20carrying%20case%20or%20discreet%20covers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20understand%20power%20can%20mean%20different%20things%20to%20different%20people.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20highest%20vibration%20mode%20on%20each%20toy%20should%20pack%20a%20serious%20punch.%20No%20tickling%20here%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20talking%20fast%2C%20big-time%20vibrations.%20But%20here's%20the%20rub%3A%20Those%20vibrations%20shouldn't%20extend%20up%20the%20arm%20of%20the%20vibrator.%20They%20should%20stay%20localized%20to%20the%20tip%20to%20deliver%20maximum%20impact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELength%20of%20charge%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI'm%20less%20interested%20in%20how%20long%20vibrators%20take%20to%20charge%20since%20I%20always%20recommend%20charging%20them%20overnight.%20I'm%20more%20interested%20in%20how%20long%20a%20full%20charge%20lasts%2C%20as%20there's%20nothing%20I%20hate%20more%20than%20reaching%20for%20a%20vibe%20I%20charged%20yesterday%20and%20finding%20it%20dead.%20So%2C%20I%20looked%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20an%20hour's%20charge%20to%20ensure%20my%20vibrator%20lasts%20more%20than%20one%20session.%20Ideally%2C%20I'm%20looking%20at%20a%20minimum%20of%20three%20sessions%20before%20it%20requires%20a%20recharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhy%20orgasms%20are%20good%20for%20your%20health%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20plenty%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Finsider.com%2Fbenefits-of-sex%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eof%20health%20benefits%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20staying%20sexually%20active%2C%20many%20of%20which%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Fbenefits-of-orgasm-for-women%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebacked%20by%20scientific%20studies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20research.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fsex-relationships%2Fis-masturbation-healthy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMasturbating%20to%20orgasm%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20a%20significant%20positive%20impact%20on%20one's%20mood%20and%20stress%20levels%20and%20can%20even%20help%20relieve%20pain%20and%20improve%20sleep.%20Reaching%20orgasm%20releases%20hormones%20like%20endorphins%2C%20oxytocin%2C%20and%20serotoni