like%20stocks%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fbond-market-crash-jpmorgan-bank-of-america-unrealized-losses-explainer-2023-11%5C%22%3Ebonds%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20commercial%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20estimated%20that%20due%20to%20declines%20in%20property%20values%20from%20rate%20hikes%20and%20remote%20work%2C%20about%2014%25%20of%20all%20loans%20and%2044%25%20of%20office%20loans%20are%20in%20negative%20equity%2C%20meaning%20current%20values%20are%20less%20than%20outstanding%20loan%20balances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%2010%25-20%25%20of%20all%20commercial%20real%20estate%20loans%20could%20default%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20low%20end%20of%20what%20the%20default%20rate%20was%20estimated%20to%20be%20during%20the%20Great%20Financial%20Crisis%20%E2%80%94%20and%20banks%20could%20see%20around%20%24160%20billion%20in%20losses%2C%20according%20to%20the%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20evidence%20suggests%20that%20if%20interest%20rates%20remain%20elevated%20and%20property%20values%20do%20not%20recover%2C%20default%20rates%20could%20potentially%20reach%20levels%20comparing%20or%20even%20surpassing%20those%20seen%20during%20the%20Great%20Recession%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20experts%20have%20also%20warned%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fcommercial-real-estate-debt-regional-banks-risk-stock-market-cre-2023-3%5C%22%3Etrouble%20for%20the%20commercial%20real%20estate%20space%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20the%20industry%20has%20around%20%241.5%20trillion%20in%20debt%20that's%20set%20to%20mature%20over%20the%20coming%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prospect%20of%20additional%20banks%20losses%20raises%20fears%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-bank-failure-what-happened-bank-run-explained-2023-3%5C%22%3Eanother%20bank%20run%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20one%20that%2