r%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Janata%20Dal-United%20(JDU)%20Supremo%20Nitish%20Kumar%20was%20%26quot%3Bunhappy%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20proposal%20of%20Congress%20Chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20as%20the%20Prime%20Ministerial%20candidate%2C%20Congress%20dismissed%20the%20same%20stating%20that%20the%20meeting%20was%20concluded%20on%20a%20%26quot%3Bgood%20note%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20meeting%20went%20on%20for%20five%20to%20six%20hours.%20The%20meeting%20was%20crucial%20and%20effective.%20It%20was%20concluded%20on%20a%20good%20note.%20If%20some%20media%20reports%20are%20claiming%20that%20Nitish%20Kumarji%20was%20unhappy%20over%20the%20meeting%2C%20there%20might%20be%20some%20'vested%20interest'%20but%20I%20reckon%20that%20he%20is%20the%20convener%20of%20the%20alliance%20and%20he%20will%20make%20it%20reach%20its%20destination%26quot%3B%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Ghulam%20Ahmad%20Mir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20fourth%20meeting%20of%20the%20Opposition's%20'Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20bloc%20concluded%20with%20the%20passing%20of%20the%20resolution%20on%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%20and%20the%20suspension%20of%20MPs%20from%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20also%20took%20place%20amid%20escalating%20political%20tensions%20between%20the%20Opposition%20and%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%2C%20triggered%20by%20the%20demand%20for%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah's%20statement%20on%20the%20recent%20Parliament%20security%20breach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2028%20parties%20participated%20in%20our%20fourth%20meeting%20and%20kept%20their%20thoughts%20before%20the%20committee%20of%20the%20alliance.%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20that%20a%20resolution%20has%20been%20passed%20that%20the%20suspension%20of%20MPs%20is%20undemocratic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20loom%20just%20four%20months%20away%2C%20the%20allocation%20of%20seats%20becomes%20pivotal%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20especially%20after%20recent%20electoral%20setbacks.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20has%20not%20reached%20a%20consensus%20on%20the%20bloc's%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate.%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20stated%20that%20any%20decision%20on%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%20would%20be%20made%20after%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20such%20information%20has%20come%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20the%20floor%20leaders%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20held%20a%20meeting%20at%20Congress%20President%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge's%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20out%20of%20the%20meeting%2C%20CPI(M)%20MP%20Elamaram%20Kareem%20informed%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20will%20hold%20a%20protest%20on%20December%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BINDIA%20alliance%20has%20decided%20to%20hold%20a%20protest%20dharna%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20(Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance)%20parties%20are%20seeking%20to%20put%20up%20a%20united%20challenge%20against%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20The%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20joint%20opposition%20convened%20in%20Patna%20on%20June%2023%20and%20the%20second%20meeting%20was%20held%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20July%2017-18.%20The%20third%20meeting%20happened%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20August%2031-September%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Mumbai%20meeting%2C%20the%20opposition%20parties%20adopted%20resolutions%20to%20collectively%20contest%20the%20upcoming%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20while%20announcing%20that%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20would%20be%20finalized%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20in%20a%20spirit%20of%20give-and-take%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%