ry%20that%20he%20shares%20over%20coffee%20at%20the%20vibrant%20Khan%20Academy%20offices%20in%20Mountain%20View%2C%20California.%20He%20doesn't%20mind%20finding%20me%20a%20coffee%20mug%20from%20the%20office%20pantry%2C%20I%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmrita%20Gandhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Students%20routinely%20send%20thank-you%20notes%20to%20tell%20you%20how%20grateful%20they%20are%20for%20getting%20them%20through%20math%20at%20school.%20How%20does%20that%20feel%20even%20today%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESal%20Khan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%C2%A0Any%20entrepreneurial%20journey%2C%20for-profit%20or%20non-profit%2C%20is%20very%20hard.%20I%20remember%20those%20first%20few%20months%20when%20I%20was%20getting%20rejected%20by%20lots%20of%20philanthropists%2C%20and%20I%20was%20living%20off%20my%20savings.%20That's%20what%20gave%20me%20the%20energy%20to%20keep%20working%20on%20it...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmrita%20Gandhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sal%2C%20you%20have%20a%20huge%20footprint%20with%20what%20you%20are%20doing.%20Millions%20of%20kids%20around%20the%20world%20are%20learning%20from%20Khan%20Academy%20and%20hundreds%20of%20schools%20use%20your%20tools%20to%20teach.%20Yet%20it%20all%20started%20with%20a%20very%20small%20real%20estate%2C%20your%20walk-in%20closet%20where%20you%20recorded%20many%20of%20your%20videos%20and%20still%20record%20many%20of%20your%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESal%20Khan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20There's%20a%20window%2C%20you%20can%20touch%20both%20walls%20without%20spreading%20your%20hands%2C%20so%20it%20is%20small%2C%20but%20people%20shouldn't%20feel%20too%20sorry%20for%20me%20(laughs).%20It%20is%20a%20nice%20closet%20and%20now%20definitely%20has%20some%20folklore%20to%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmrita%20Gandhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Sal%20you%20didn't%20need%20to%20do%20math%20lessons%20for%20free%20for%20people%2C%20when%20you%20were%20already%20on%20the%20path%20to%20have%20a%20very%20conventional%2C%20successful%20lucrative%20career%20after%20MIT%2C%20Harvard%2C%20and%20working%20in%20a%20hedge%20fund.%20Not%20everyone%20knows%20that%20it%20began%20with%20your%20cousin%2C%20Nadia%2C%20and%20how%20you%20started%20helping%20her%20remotely%20with%20her%20math%20lessons.%20So%20that's%20how%20it%20started%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESal%20Khan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Even%20when%20I%20was%20working%20on%20my%20job%2C%20at%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind%20I%20had%20nascent%20ideas%20about%20how%20education%20could%20be%20improved%20and%20the%20coolest%20second%20career%20could%20be%20for%20me%20to%20be%20a%20Dumbledore-type%20figure%20with%20my%20own%20Hogwarts%20and%20it%20was%20a%20daydream.%20In%202004%2C%20I%20was%20a%20year%20out%20of%20business%20school%2C%20and%20it%20came%20out%20of%20a%20conversation%20that%20my%2012-year-old%20cousin%20needed%20help%20with%20math.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20talked%20to%20Nadia%20and%20she%20was%20(%20struggling%20with)%20unit%20conversions.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BNadia%2C%20I%20am%20a%20hundred%20per%20cent%20sure%20you%20can%20figure%20it%20out.%26quot%3B%20I%20started%20working%20with%20her%20remotely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20the%20issues%20were%20her%20confidence.%20She%20got%20caught%20up%20with%20her%20class%20and%20got%20ahead%20of%20her%20class%20and%20I%20became%20her%20tiger%20cousin.%20I%20called%20up%20her%20school%20and%20I%20said%20I%20think%20Nadia%20should%20be%20able%20to%20retake%20her%20placement%20test.%20This%20was%20a%20girl%20having%20trouble%20with%207th%20grade%20math.%20By%20the%20summer%2C%20she%20was%20taking%20calculus%20at%20the%20local%20university...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmrita%20Gandhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20free%20component%20of%20the%20education%20you%20provide%2C%20that%20it%20should%20be%20available%20for%20free%2C%20clearly%20means%20a%20lot%20to%20you.%20Why%20is%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESal%20Khan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20worked%20in%20a%20hedge%20fund%2C%20I%20am%20not%20like%20an%20angel%20(%20laughs).%20I%20believe%20in%20general%20and%20free%20markets.%20But%2C%20there%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20places%20in%20our%20lives%20where%20market%20forces%20do%20not%20lead%20to%20outcomes%20that%20are%20consistent%20with%20our%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20places%20are%20probably%20education%20and%20health.%20You%20can%20have%20a%20for-profit%20sector%20there%20that%20gets%20better%20at%20marketing%20rather%20than%20making%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20product%20really%20strong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20student%20is%20struggling%2C%20they%20can%20jump%20into%20Khan%20Academy%20and%20get%20the%20support%20they%20need.%20Science%2C%20middle%20school%2C%20high%20school%2C%20early%20biology%2C%20physics%2C%20even%20humanities%2C%20and%20grammar%2C%20it%20is%20all%20there.%20It%20is%20all%20free%2C%20hopefully%2C%20people%20realize%20there%20is%20no%20catch%20here%2C%20it%20is%20funded%20with%20philanthropy%2C%20and%20it%20is%20truly%20the%20most%20efficacious%20platform%20out%20there.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20folks%20willing%20to%20charge%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20and%20in%20places%2C%20it%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20very%20big%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmrita%20Gandhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20You%20have%20chosen%20an%20unconventional%20path%20for%20yourself%20that%20doesn't%20prioritize%20profits.%20Was%20that%20hard%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESal%20Khan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20quit%20my%20day%20job.%20We%20live%20out%20here%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Silicon%20Valley.%20There%20were%20some%20VCs%20(Venture%20Capitalists)%20who%20would%20reach%20out%20to%20me%20and%20say%20we'll%20write%20you%20a%20check%2C%20and%20you%20can%20start%20supporting%20your%20family.%20And%20I%20was%20intrigued%2C%20if%20not%20a%20little%20desperate.%20The%20first%20meeting%20was%20interesting%20but%20the%20second%20and%20third%20meetings%20were%20like%20-%20we%20can%20give%20people%20this%20for%20free%2C%20but%20we'll%20upsell%20people%20this%20other%20stuff.%20And%20I%20would%20think%20about%20the%20kind%20of%20(appreciation)%20notes%20that%20you%20just%20mentioned%20-%20if%20we%20did%20that%2C%20probably%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20these%20people%20getting%20transformative%20positive%20impact%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20the%20decision%20we%20made%20to%20make%20this%20a%20non-profit.%20Let's%20make%20sure%20this%20works%2C%20let's%20make%20sure%20it's%20engaging%20to%20students%20and%20families%20and%20teachers%2C%20and%20let's%20make%20sure%20it%20is%20accessible...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20have%20enough%2C%20I%20have%20my%20health%2C%20I%20have%20a%20wonderful%20family%2C%20and%20two%20cars%20in%20the%20garage.%20If%20you%20can%20get%20to%20work%20on%20something%20and%20get%20notes%20like%20that%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20better%20than%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmrita%20Gandhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20You%20grew%20up%20near%20New%20Orleans%2C%20Louisiana%20and%20there%20is%20a%20story%20about%20when%20you%20were%20growing%20up%20and%20you%20were%20doing%20your%20mom's%20taxes%20and%20you%20realized%20that%20she%20was%20pretty%20much%20earning%20minimum%20wage.%20She%20raised%20you%20and%20your%20sister%2C%20singly.%20Did%20your%20family%20have%20a%20big%20impact%20on%20you%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20are%20today%20giving%20away%20math%20for%20free%3F%20Others%20might%20have%20said%20when%20I%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20earn%2C%20I%20am%20going%20to%20earn%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESal%20Khan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20My%20father%20was%20a%20physician%2C%20and%20in%201968%2C%20came%20here%20(to%20America)%20and%20had%20an%20arranged%20marriage%20to%20my%20mom.%20Then%20something%20unusual%20for%20South%20Asian%20families%20happened.%20My%20parents%20separated.%20My%20father%20was%20going%20through%20some%20mental%20health%20issues.%20I%20never%20really%20met%20him.%20I%20met%20him%20one%20day%20when%20I%20was%2013%20and%20he%20passed%20away%20when%20I%20was%2014.%20%C2%A0My%20mum%20raised%20my%20sister%20and%20I%20as%20a%20single%20parent.%20The%20main%20job%20she%20had%20access%20to%20was%20to%20be%20a%20cashier%20at%20a%20convenience%20store.%20When%20I%20was%20very%20young%2C%20as%20she%20didn't%20have%20childcare%2C%20I%20remember%20her%20job%20was...%20she%20had%20the%20keys%20to%20this%20vending%20machine%20and%20would%20take%20out%20the%20change.%20To%20her%20credit%2C%20we%20never%20felt%20poor.%20But%20every%20now%20and%20then%20it%20would%20hit%20us.%20Like%20we%20didn't%20have%20health%20care.%20One%20of%20my%20father's%20colleagues%20would%20see%20us%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20high%20school%20came%20around%2C%20I%20asked%20my%20older%20sister%20where%20she%20wanted%20to%20go%20to%20college%2C%20and%20she%20said%20Brown%20(University).%20And%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20crazy%3F%20The%20tuition%20is%20twice%20what%20we%20make%20in%20a%20year%26quot%3B.%20She%20explained%20what%20financial%20aid%20is.%20While%20filing%20taxes%20to%20show%20you%20needed%20financial%20aid%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20our%20income%20and%20wondered%20how%20we%20were%20managing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmrita%20Gandhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20You%20graduated%20from%20MIT%20yourself%20and%20went%20to%20Harvard%20Business%20School%2C%20yet%20you%20gave%20up%20that%20lucrative%20career%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESal%20Khan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20it%20was%20my%20turn%20to%20go%20to%20college%20and%20business%20school%2C%20I%20had%20a%20chip%20on%20my%20shoulder%20that%20I%20am%20not%20going%20to%20have%20financial%20insecurity%20and%20I%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20is%20off%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20by%20the%20time%20Khan%20Academy%20became%20a%20thing%20I%20was%20working%20in%20a%20hedge%20fund%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20pay%20down%20my%20debt%20and%20was%20feeling%20more%20secure%2C%20but%20we%20were%20not%20fully%20secure.%20But%20at%20some%20point%2C%20you%20have%20to%20ask%20yourself%2C%20how%20much%20do%20you%20really%20need%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20think%20beyond%20a%20certain%20amount%20you%20go%20from%20zero%20to%20some%20figure.%20Money%20matters%20a%20lot.%20You%20have%20the%20basics%20to%20support%20the%20family%20and%20go%20on%20vacation%2C%20%C2%A0beyond%20that%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20gets%20you%20a%20lot.%20Instead%2C%20if%20you%20can%20work%20on%20something%20interesting%20with%20good%20people%2C%20it%20doesn't%20get%20better%20that...%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmrita%20Gandhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20What%20was%20the%20reaction%20of%20your%20family%20when%20you%20decided%20to%20quit%20your%20job%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESal%20Khan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20had%20some%20savings%20that%20we%20were%20saving%20on%20a%20down%20payment%20for%20a%20house.%20My%20wife%20had%20a%20medical%20fellowship%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20a%20lot.%20Our%20first%20child%20had%20just%20been%20born%3B%20my%20mother-in-law%20had%20just%20moved%20into%20our%20house.%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20mixed%20reactions%20from%20family%20members%20on%20quitting%20my%20day%20job%20because%20it%20was%20a%20good%20job.%20(Laughs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmrita%20Gandhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20anxiety%20about%20kids%20getting%20into%20the%20right%20college.%20There%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20when%20parents%20feel%20their%20kids%20aren't%20studying%20enough.%20There%20is%20pressure%20with%20extracurricular.%20What%20is%20your%20general%20advice%20in%20this%20era%20of%20heightened%20competition%20for%20getting%20in%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESal%20Khan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20part%20of%20my%20answer%20will%20be%20a%20little%20bit%20traditional.%20It%20is%20important%20that%20children%20have%20a%20really%20solid%20academic%20foundation.%20As%20a%20parent%2C%20it%20is%20good%20to%20sometimes%20take%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20action%20to%20make%20sure%20they%20have%20a%20fundamental%20foundation%20in%20math%2C%20reading%2C%20and%20writing.%20It%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20dramatic%20or%20hours%20and%20hours%20-%20that's%20when%20it%20gets%20unhealthy%20for%20the%20kid's%20mental%20health.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20have%20enough%20space%20in%20their%20lives%20to%20develop%20authentic%20passions%20rather%20than%20doing%20things%20just%20to%20get%20into%20college.%20College%20admission%20officers%20in%20America%20are%20really%20good%20at%20being%20able%20to%20distinguish%20between%20authenticity%2C%20at%20least%20here%20where%20extracurriculars%20mean%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmrita%20Gandhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20You%20have%20embraced%20AI%20in%20a%20big%20way.%20Yet%20many%20educators%20have%20been%20reticent.%20What%20makes%20you%20embrace%20it%20so%20readily%20while%20others%20have%20reservations%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESal%20Khan%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20those%20reservations%20are%20legitimate.%20Open%20AI%20reached%20out%20to%20us%20over%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20well%20before%20ChatGPT%2C%20and%20they%20showed%20us%20GPT%204.%20%C2%A0When%20we%20saw%20what%20it%20was%20capable%20of%2C%20we%20thought%20it%20was%20very%20compelling%2C%20but%20a%20lot%20of%20fears%20around%20errors%2C%20cheating%2C%20around%20bias%2C%20we%20saw%20them%20as%20well%2C%20and%20we%20started%20having%20these%20debates.%20We%20thought%20that%20if%20we%20could%20change%20some%20of%20the%20fears%20into%20features%20and%20mitigate%20the%20risks%20by%20maximizing%20positives%2C%20we%20should%20do%20that.%20We%20believe%20we%20should%20not%20just%20use%20technology%20because%20it%20is%20cool.%20We%20should%20have%20a%20clear%20goal%20of%20what%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20solve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEverything%20we%20do%2C%20if%20we%20look%20at%20the%20whole%20narrative%20of%20Khan%