2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fi-will-prevent-world-war-iii-donald-trump-during-presidential-campaign-rally%2Famp_articleshow%2F106160665.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fi-will-prevent-world-war-iii-donald-trump-during-presidential-campaign-rally%2Famp_articleshow%2F106160665.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Can%20Help%20Find%20Your%20Missing%20Child%26quot%3B%3A%20How%20Tech%20Grad%20Conned%20900%20Parents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECyber-criminals%20aren't%20exactly%20known%20for%20their%20compassion%2C%20but%20what%20this%2028-year-old%20did%20may%20just%20be%20a%20new%20low.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20graduate%20in%20computer%20application%20has%20been%20arrested%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20for%20preying%20on%20the%20grief%20of%20over%20900%20families%20from%20Delhi-NCR%20whose%20children%20had%20gone%20missing.%20He%20would%20get%20the%20parents'%20details%20from%20a%20missing%20persons'%20register%2C%20call%20them%20up%20and%20pose%20as%20a%20police%20official.%20He%20would%20then%20claim%20that%20the%20child%20has%20been%20found%20in%20a%20different%20city%20and%20ask%20the%20parents%20to%20transfer%20some%20money%20to%20help%20the%20cops%20get%20them%20back%2C%20a%20police%20official%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elated%20parents%20would%20transfer%20the%20sum%20and%20look%20forward%20to%20finally%20reuniting%20with%20their%20children%2C%20only%20to%20find%20out%20that%20they%20had%20been%20scammed.%20They%20would%20also%20have%20to%20confront%20their%20grief%20all%20over%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20The%20Scam%20Worked%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2015%2C%20the%20Wazirabad%20police%20station%20in%20north%20Delhi%20received%20a%20complaint%20from%20a%20father%20in%20the%20area%20to%20report%20that%20his%20daughter%20had%20gone%20missing.%20After%20noting%20down%20the%20information%2C%20the%20police%20officials%20registered%20a%20report%20and%20then%20uploaded%20the%20details%20of%20the%20child%20and%20her%20family%20to%20the%20missing%20person's%20portal%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20then%20received%20a%20call%20from%20a%20man%2C%20who%20claimed%20that%20their%20daughter%20had%20been%20found%20and%20they%20should%20transfer%20Rs%208%2C000%20using%20a%20QR%20code%20he%20had%20sent%20to%20help%20get%20her%20back.%20The%20amount%20was%20transferred%2C%20but%20the%20parents%20never%20heard%20from%20the%20person%20again.%20A%20complaint%20was%20filed%20and%20the%20police%20formed%20a%20team%20to%20trace%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMultiple%20Instances%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3Bin%20the%20past%20few%20days%2C%20we%20received%20multiple%20written%20and%20verbal%20complaints%20from%20parents%20in%20the%20North%20Delhi%20district%20that%20their%20missing%20child%20had%20been%20found%20and%20they%20had%20paid%20money%20to%20police%20personnel%20but%20they%20got%20no%20response%20after%20that%2C%20or%20were%20not%20reunited%20with%20their%20child.%20During%20our%20investigation%2C%20we%20found%20out%20about%20a%20gang%20that%20would%20retrieve%20the%20numbers%20of%20parents%20of%20missing%20children%20from%20publicly%20available%20databases%20and%20call%20them%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Meena%2C%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%2C%20North%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20databases%20include%20ZIPNet%20(Zonal%20Integrated%20Police%20Network)%20and%20other%20such%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Meena%20said%20the%20accused%20would%20pose%20as%20a%20police%20officer.%20%26quot%3BHe%20would%20say%20the%20child%20has%20been%20recovered%20and%20ask%20for%20a%20small%20sum%20saying%20that%20the%20child%20was%20in%20other%20cities%2C%20like%20Dehradun%2C%20and%20the%20money%20was%20needed%20to%20get%20them%20back.%20The%20parents