C%20the%20union%20government%20delayed%20Justice%20Mridul%E2%80%99s%20transfer%2C%20recommended%20on%20July%205%2C%202023%2C%20for%20over%20three%20months%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Funion-govt-appoints-manipur-hc-chief-justice-three-months-after-his-nomination%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclearing%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20on%20October%2016%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20is%20yet%20to%20act%20on%20Justice%20Bhatnagar%E2%80%99s%20transfer%20which%20the%20collegium%20recommended%20on%20August%2010%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20lawyers%20said%20it%20was%20due%20to%20this%20state%20of%20limbo%20that%20the%20special%20bench%20in%20the%20conspiracy%20case%20did%20not%20hear%20arguments%20in%20the%20remaining%20cases%20after%20Justice%20Mridul%E2%80%99s%20transfer%20was%20recommended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20both%20the%20judges%20in%20the%20special%20bench%20were%20recommended%20for%20transfer%20in%20July%20and%20August%2C%20there%20was%20uncertainty%20over%20when%20the%20transfers%20would%20actually%20go%20through%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bora%2C%20Fatima%E2%80%99s%20counsel%2C%20told%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EArticle%2014%3Cem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20might%20have%20swayed%20the%20bench%20to%20resist%20hearing%20the%20cases%20after%20July%202023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20perspective%20of%20ordinary%20litigants%2C%20like%20these%20accused%2C%20delays%20and%20uncertainties%20in%20judicial%20appointments%20and%20transfers%20mean%20long%20periods%20of%20waiting%20to%20have%20meaningful%20hearings%2C%20said%20Bora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20members%20of%20the%20accused%20were%20hopeful%20that%20the%20new%20bench%20that%20will%20hear%20the%20nine%20cases%20afresh%20will%20deliver%20its%20verdict%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20sure%20we%20will%20get%20justice.%20Everyone%20does%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Saima%2C%20Saleem%E2%80%