with%20%E2%80%9Cegress%20openings%E2%80%9D%20for%20%E2%80%9Cescape%E2%80%9D%20during%20an%20emergency%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20instead%20recommended%20the%20original%20project%20plan%3A%20A%20dedicated%203.5m%20escape%20channel%20separated%20by%20a%20concrete%20barrier%20from%20a%207m%20carriageway%20meant%20for%20two-way%20traffic%20inside%20a%20D-shaped%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20this%20design%20was%20later%20modified%20during%20the%20construction%2C%20apparently%20for%20better%20space%20utilisation%20and%20traffic%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20leaving%20an%20escape%20channel%20on%20the%20left%2C%20we%20put%20the%20divider%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20tunnel%20for%20single-way%20traffic%20on%20either%20side.%20This%20created%20more%20space%20for%20traffic%20and%20eliminated%20the%20risk%20of%20head-on%20collisions%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20project%20engineer%20told%20the%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20tunnelling%20expert%20involved%20in%20the%20rescue%20operation%20last%20month%20pointed%20out%20that%20a%20total%20blockage%20of%20the%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20made%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20positioning%20of%20the%20divider%E2%80%9D%20immaterial%20and%20only%20a%20separate%20evacuation%20tunnel%20could%20have%20helped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20situation%20like%20this%20(collapse)%20requires%20a%20separate%20evacuation%20duct%20running%20next%20to%20the%20main%20tunnel%20with%20access%20at%20regular%20intervals%2C%20or%20a%20few%20lateral%20inclined%20escape%20adits%20rising%20to%20the%20ground%20surface.%20Having%20an%20escape%20passage%20in%20the%20same%20tunnel%20helps%20during%20traffic%20or%20fire%20incidents%2C%20but%20not%20if%20there%20is%20a%20total%20blockage%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20expert%20told%20%3Cem%3EIE%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20construction%20time%20and%20cost%20required%20is%20more%20for%20two%20tunnels%2C%20two%20portals%20and%20two%20sets%20of%20ventilation%20systems.%20This%20system%20is%20best%20suited%20in%20case%20of%20heavy%20traffic%20volume%20but%20at%20current%20location%2C%20the%20traffic%20volume%20is%20only%202000%20PCU%20(passenger%20car%20units).%20Hence%20this%20proposal%20is%20also%20not%20recommended%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20EIA%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-collapse-warning-environment-development%5C%22%3EIf%20Lessons%20Are%20Not%20Learnt%2C%20Expect%20More%20Silkyaras%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20submitted%20the%20208-page%20rapid%20EIA%20report%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20September%202020.%20By%20then%2C%20the%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20was%20%E2%80%9Calready%20under%20construction%20and%20more%20than%2015%25%20of%20the%20work%20has%20already%20been%20completed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20work%20was%20already%20on%2C%20the%20rapid%20EIA%20report%20reflected%20the%20project%20plan.%20For%20the%20rescue%20channel%2C%20too%2C%20it%20rejected%20the%20options%20not%20on%20the%20card.%20It%20could%20not%20have%20predicted%20that%20the%20project%20would%20go%20on%20to%20drop%20the%20escape%20channel%20altogether%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20consultant%20involved%20in%20the%20EIA%20process%20told%20the%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Silkyara-Barkot%20tunnel%20is%20part%20of%20the%20889-km%20Char%20Dham%20project.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%C2%A0%20government%20split%20the%20project%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fchar-dham-highway-project-shouldve-undergone-impact-assessment-v-k-saraswat%5C%22%3E53%20separate%20sections%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20none%20over%20100%20kilometre%20in%20length%2C%20and%20evaded%20the%20need%20for%20an%20environmental%20impact%20assessment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn